\end_inset

 is the ratio of the amount of useful energy obtained to the amount of energy
 that was needed to produce it.
 If the EROEI is less than 1, then more energy has been consumed than has
 been gained.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Since energy is required not only in extracting a fuel, but also in refining,
 transportation,
\begin_inset space \thinspace{}
\end_inset

